entities.name: Auto.fun
entities.description: A platform that facilitates the creation and launch of tokens, offering features such as token-gated chat, vanity contract addresses, and AI generation for tokens. It aims to provide an alternative to platforms like pump.fun and has focused on UI/UX improvements.

entities.name: ElizaOS
entities.description: A development platform focused on AI agents and operating systems. Its development includes progress on v2 with multi-agent capabilities and improved APIs, with a focus on memory issues and enhanced agent knowledge.

entities.name: Squidllora
entities.description: A new trading agent announced by @elizaOS, powered by @AlloraNetwork and elizaOS. It features real-time onchain signals and swarm-based agents.

entities.name: PostgreSQL
entities.description: An open-source relational database management system (RDBMS) with an object-relational model. It emphasizes extensibility and SQL compliance.

entities.name: Raydium
entities.description: A decentralized exchange (DEX) and automated market maker (AMM) built on the Solana blockchain. It aims to provide high-speed transactions and low fees.

entities.name: Jupiter
entities.description: A decentralized exchange aggregator for Solana, aiming to provide users with the best prices for their swaps by routing through various liquidity sources.

entities.name: eliza.how
entities.description: The main website for the Eliza platform, which experienced downtime.

entities.name: docs.eliza.how
entities.description: The documentation website for the Eliza platform, which remained accessible while the main website was down.

entities.name: WETH
entities.description: Wrapped Ether, an ERC-20 token that represents Ether (ETH) on Ethereum-compatible blockchains. It allows Ether to be used in DeFi applications that only support ERC-20 tokens.

entities.name: SOL
entities.description: The native cryptocurrency of the Solana blockchain, a high-performance blockchain platform designed for fast, scalable, and decentralized applications.

entities.name: eliza.gg
entities.description: A service related to Eliza that was reported to be down.

entities.name: Osint
entities.description: An individual providing information about Auto.fun and its features.

entities.name: Spartan V2
entities.description: An updated version of the Spartan project, which includes exclusive plugins for community-investing, autonomous trading, and market intel gathering.
